citus-ha (2.1.0) testing; urgency=low
 
  * Fix: wait until postgres is ready after pg_ctl start before connecting
 
  * Fix default HBA connection privileges from coordinator to worker nodes
 
  * Feature: allow formations to run without secondaries
 
  * Added nodename and nodeport to the output of `citusha show state`
 
  * Use absolute pgdata path for monitor config and keeper config
 
  * Deduplicate pg_ctl if the same is on the path twice

 -- Nils Dijk <nils@citusdata.com>  Thu, 18 Apr 2019 17:43:00 +0100

